- Container ke andar 2 divs honge:
Left side → Text content + vertical line
Right side → Images

Jab user scroll karega:
Left side wali vertical line par ek white indicator/character 
niche move karega,jaise progress show ho rahi ho.
Usi scroll progress ke according text change hota rahega 
(GSAP timeline se).Saath hi same timeline mein:
Right side ki images bhi change hongi.
Har text section ke saath uski corresponding image display hogi.

- Matlab ek hi GSAP timeline scroll ko control karegi:
Line Progress → Text Change → Image Change, sab scroll ke 
saath synchronize rahenge jab tak pinned section complete na ho 
